<title>四川舰，电弹已就位！</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D%E8%88%B0%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B5%E5%BC%B9%E5%B7%B2%E5%B0%B1%E4%BD%8D%EF%BC%81</link>
